articles.title: WTA Finals: Iga Swiatek storms to glory with straight-sets win over Jessica Pegula in Cancun - Sky Sports
articles.description: Iga Swiatek dominated American Jessica Pegula 6-1 6-0 to win the WTA Finals and regain her world No 1 ranking.
articles.content:
Iga Swiatek dominated American Jessica Pegula 6-1 6-0 to win the season-ending WTA Finals in Cancun on Monday and regain her world No 1 ranking from Aryna Sabalenka.
